	<h2>Continuing Work</h2>
	<p>We intend to continue developing our product after the end of this project, to ensure that our clients continue to recieve the best possible product. We will consider the following:</p>
	<ul>
	  <li>Further development of our programming interface.</li>
	  <li>Target the next levels of education.</li>
	  <li>Produce Pre-made educational content</li>
	  <li>Release our product as a Full End-User development platform</li>
	</ul>
	<hr>
	<h2>Future Marketing</h2>
	<p>Going forward, our first marketing stage will focus on relatively low-cost strategies, such as magazine editorial content, attending local trade fairs, and online guerrilla strategies through forums and blogs.</p><br>
	<p>After achieving success in our initial stage, we intend to further develop our strategy into more costly areas of marketing, such as physical adverts, larger international trade shows, and potentially traditional online marketing.</p>
	<hr>
	<p>Read more in our <a href="static/future_marketing.pdf"><em>Future Plan</em></a></p>
